---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Solutions & Services" description="Solving medical scrub manufacturing pain points. Low MOQs, fast lead times, and custom branding for healthcare brands.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-center italic">Solving Your Manufacturing Challenges</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-20 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg italic">At Yilong Scrubs, we don't just take orders; we solve the common "pain points" that healthcare brands face in today’s competitive market.</p>
    
    <!-- Pain Point 1: Low MOQ -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center mb-32">
      <div>
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-600 font-bold rounded-full text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic">Pain Point #1: The "High MOQ" Barrier</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic">Struggling with excessive minimum order requirements?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">Most factories demand 500+ sets per color, making it impossible for startups or niche clinics to launch their brand.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-primary/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-primary">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-primary text-xl mb-4 italic">Our Solution: Scalable Growth</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed italic">We offer an industry-leading low MOQ starting at just <span class="font-bold text-primary">10 sets per color</span>. Test the market, grow your collection, and scale at your own pace without the inventory risk.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A33d7ea38935d4a1ba4b7a78911420840r.png" alt="Flexible Ordering" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pain Point 2: Lead Time -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center mb-32">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A3e81149be9164a8087fe8da73854d6313.png" alt="Fast Collaboration" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 font-bold rounded-full text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic">Pain Point #2: The "Slow Response" Trap</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic">Losing market momentum due to slow lead times?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">In healthcare, speed matters. Waiting 3 months for production or 2 weeks for a sample response kills your competitiveness.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-secondary/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-secondary">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-secondary text-xl mb-4 italic">Our Solution: Accelerated Timeline</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-600 italic">
            <li><span class="font-bold">3-7 Day Sampling:</span> From idea to prototype in under a week.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">15-30 Day Bulk Delivery:</span> Fast-track production for global shipping.</li>
            <li><span class="font-bold">Transparent Communication:</span> Direct access to Marvin and the manufacturing floor.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pain Point 3: Brand Identity -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center mb-32">
      <div>
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 font-bold rounded-full text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic">Pain Point #3: The "Brand Identity" Gap</div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic">Tired of selling generic, unbranded scrubs?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">If you can't differentiate your product, you’re forced to compete on price alone. Generic labels won’t build long-term customer loyalty.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-indigo-600">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-indigo-600 text-xl mb-4 italic">Our Solution: Full-Suite Customization</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed italic italic">We provide a complete branding toolkit: Private labels (neck & side), custom-branded hangtags, and premium customized polybag/box packaging to ensure your brand stands out on every hospital floor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-slate-100 aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden border border-slate-100">
        <div class="p-12 h-full flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-200">
           <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-48 h-48" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z" />
           </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-[4rem] p-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8 italic">Ready to solve your manufacturing headaches?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 italic leading-relaxed">Let's discuss how Yilong Scrubs can streamline your production and help you build a profitable medical apparel brand. 20 years of experience is at your service.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-black text-xl hover:bg-blue-800 transition shadow-xl uppercase tracking-widest">Connect with Marvin</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>